{"tid":918263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[補選]泛民係咪自己口中嘅焦土派?","createTime":"2018-11-27T05:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T14:47:41.000Z","uid":47359,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"914e2e022e8e3620fda8dda0c48b5099587f90b2","tid":918263,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"有票唔投唔阻止惡法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017年6月17日，沙中線8.47億追加撥款以6票之差獲得通過，10名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F162225&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88rhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=85aae447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年3月22日，立法會審議 1131億臨時撥款，在全體泛民議員缺席下，議案只花兩分鐘，由不足十名建制派議員在不記名投票下贊成通過。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fbkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88rhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d0ceab9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月26日，工務小組審議17.85億元朗行人天橋撥款，議案以3票之差獲得通過，5名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fv201805261.pdf&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88rhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=bc27036d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月25日，林卓廷提出就「升降機維修保養對市民安全進行辯論議案」以6票之差未獲通過，7名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fvoting%2Fhc20180525-voting-ec.pdf&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88rhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e484ab7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月31日，建制派「共建粵港澳大灣區」動議順利通過，地方選區輸2票，2名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fvoting%2Fv20180530.pdf&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88rhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7740045e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"74068f8a7ee1f5732658c25bce1f89ef2d7697d1","tid":918263,"uid":26329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:33:04.000Z","msg":"做港獨之父果套，暗焦"},{"pid":"a7025f819867c4090bf2b8568d0753f06eeec7f5","tid":918263,"uid":153239,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"貼呢張啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/211101_61b1a829df455ea9d2859cbc85206f2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F16%2F211101_61b1a829df455ea9d2859cbc85206f2a.jpg&h=175d7f22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cbb9498cec49068a78c510c72c3f6ad46729a02","tid":918263,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"是L但啦，總之香港人係咪都食屎，梗係要拉埋my香港既一齊食先夠公平"},{"pid":"ca4987e66aa21c1eddfab2478f94652ac903633c","tid":918263,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"佢地係至之死地而後生<br />\n焦土派個d叫焦土，唔同架ok?<br />\n販民一路以來缺席、贊成都係突顯緊